description:
In this week's mini episode, Kate and Doree dive right into listener calls. They talk about peach fuzz (both light and dark), tiny razors, and making peace with mustaches. Kate gives her Doogie Howser-inspired lip care routine and they both discuss self care tips for extroverts.

For more info, visit forever35podcast.com. To leave a voicemail, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
